text: Borohrádek (; ) is a town in Rychnov nad Kněžnou District in the Hradec Králové Region of the Czech Republic. It has about 2,100 inhabitants. It is located southeast of Hradec Králové and east of Prague. ==Admninistrative parts== The village of Šachov is an administrative part of Borohrádek. ==History== The first written notice about Borohrádek is from year 1342. ==References== ==External links== * *Official website Category:Cities and towns in the Czech Republic Category:Populated places in Rychnov nad Kněžnou District
